text: Gerda Kieninger (21 February 1951 - 22 January 2020) was a German politician. She was a member of the Social Democratic Party of Germany. She was born in Cologne. Kieninger was a member of the Landtag of North Rhine-Westphalia from 1995 to 2017. Kieninger died in Cologne on 22 January 2020 at the age of 68.Awo-Vorsitzende Gerda Kieninger ist gestorben ==References== Category:1951 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Politicians from Cologne Category:Politicians of the Social Democratic Party of Germany
